sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Dev as 👤 Blueprint Push (Main)
    participant L1 as 🏗️ L1: System Foundations
    participant L15 as 📦 L1.5: Runtime Foundations
    participant L2 as ⚙️ L2: Assembly
    participant Reg as 🏘️ GitHub Container Registry
    participant Security as 🛡️ Security Gate
    
    Dev->>L1: Trigger foundations build
    activate L1
    L1->>L1: Compile (glibc, openssl, certs)
    L1->>Security: SAST + SBOM + Cosign
    Security-->>L1: Pass
    L1->>Reg: Push System Artifacts
    deactivate L1
    
    Reg->>L15: Trigger Runtime Foundations
    activate L15
    L15->>Reg: Pull L1 Artifacts
    L15->>L15: Compile (libffi, ncurses, xml2)
    L15->>Security: SAST + SBOM + Cosign
    Security-->>L15: Pass
    L15->>Reg: Push Library Artifacts
    deactivate L15
    
    Reg->>L2: Trigger Assembly
    activate L2
    L2->>Reg: Pull L1 + L1.5 Artifacts
    L2->>L2: Construct Runtimes (Python, Java, etc.)
    L2->>Security: Sign OCI Manifest + SLSA
    Security-->>L2: Pass
    L2->>Reg: Push Final Images
    deactivate L2
